description: |
  Docker integration tools for AutoGen.
  Contains scripts for Docker Model Runner integration, container management,
  and Docker extension updates. Includes utilities for optimizing Docker
  configuration for high-performance computing, particularly for GPU-accelerated
  workloads and AI model inference with NVIDIA GPU passthrough support.

